steps.userPrompt:
Analyze the following request and produce a triage report:

Title: {{title}}
Body: {{body}}

Provide: 1) Category (bug, feature-request, question, incident, other). 2) Urgency (critical, high, medium, low). 3) Key entities mentioned (people, systems, services). 4) One-sentence summary. 5) Suggested next actions (2-3 bullet points).
